title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 30 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 30 2022
description:
Trump continues to respond to Cassidy Hutchinson's testimony. If Trump's so bad, why do they always have to lie about him? Clay confesses to voting for Gary Johnson in 2016. USC and UCLA to leave Pac-12 for Big Ten. South Dakota Governor Kristi Noem returns to C&B, talks abortion law in South Dakota, Biden's disastrous energy policy and her new book: "Not My First Rodeo: Lessons from the Heartland," and her support for President Trump's likely run in 2024. Clay buys a box of 1987 baseball cards -- his kids even take a tiny taste of the accompanying bubble gum!

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
